{"tid":2275544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（黑色預警）川粉出征AIT臉書？外交部抓包：機器人帳號製造台美矛盾","createTime":"2020-11-07T08:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:28:41.000Z","uid":3801,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3bef6b51f56995bf7e9ce50c56005fd4ba73cd","tid":2275544,"uid":3801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"台灣發現好多fake ac扮trump fans<br />\n唔知連登有幾多pr 5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國民主黨候選人拜登的選情見俏，可望入主白宮。大批疑似川普的支持者，竟因此「出征」美國在台協會（AIT）臉書。對此，我國外交部今（7）日回應說明，留言攻擊不少出自機器人帳號， 目的在於利用美國國內選舉來製造台美間的矛盾或國內的混亂；外交部並呼籲國內政治人物， 停止利用尚在進行中的國外選舉進行國內的政治操作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=844223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D844223&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=a85fb17f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D844223&h=45edf59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=844223</a>"},{"pid":"735c9d493551f78afd46b2dca2827c5810a6be9f","tid":2275544,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:56:06.000Z","msg":"支那出精"},{"pid":"631b0b6b3ec797fb270d28db27a81639097f3aaa","tid":2275544,"uid":3801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99ed0a0dc6330a0e8e224857362e3f27607a0ad","tid":2275544,"uid":3801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"